## Stack
- **API**: NestJS 11, Prisma 6, PostgreSQL (Neon in prod), Redis/BullMQ, JWT auth, `@nestjs/throttler`, `@nestjs/schedule`
- **Web**: Next.js 16 App Router, React 19, Tailwind 4, `next-intl` (i18n), `recharts` (analytics charts), Zod, react-hook-form
- **Worker**: Express + whatsapp-web.js (separate long-running process, port 3100)
- **BullMQ worker**: `apps/api/src/worker.ts` ‚Äî standalone process; processes WhatsApp message jobs (booking_confirm, reminder_24h, post_visit, inactive_recovery)
- **Monorepo**: npm workspaces (`apps/api`, `apps/web`, `apps/wa-worker`)

