## SEO conventions
- All Next.js pages that are server components export `generateMetadata()` pulling from `getSiteContentGroup("seo")`
- `[slug]/page.tsx` is a server wrapper around `booking-client.tsx` ‚Äî adds metadata + JSON-LD `LocalBusiness` schema
- `apps/web/src/app/sitemap.ts` ‚Äî static routes + city pages
- `apps/web/src/app/robots.ts` ‚Äî allow public, disallow `/app/`, `/api/`

## Design principles
